publisher			StormCube Games							
publish_time	 2016年3月22日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Vortex: The Gateway 是一款开放世界的生存恐怖游戏。由于进入了一个神秘的维度旋涡，你将发现自己身处外星世界。为了生存而探索、适应、建设和战斗。每天，你将在不同的时间面对该行星上的各种危险，面对不断变化的气温，饥渴交加。你可以探索景色壮观但险象环生的地方，那儿总是有土生土长的动物不断来袭。如果你想活下来，就得保持警惕，小心翼翼，不断建设，英勇作战。同时地球上的生命发生巨大的变化。什么变化呢？通过这场冒险之旅，你将知道一些底细。做最坏的准备吧！Features story mode: escape from the island survival mode: protect yourself and your injured friend a huge, diverse and fully explorable alien island with a unique atmosphere, visuals and emblematic sceneries non-generated environment, every location was designed by hand dynamic day-night cycle crafting system: harvest resources to create equipment by combining them together building system: build shelters, fences, storage, fire, etc. survival aspects: hunger, thirst, stamina, health, different temperatures, hiding living fauna: more than 30 types of harmless and dangerous animals collect food, water and hunt some of the story elements are available already atmospheric music and sounds Steam achievements						
title	 Vortex: The Gateway			
